==Spanish==

===Etymology===
Literally, "chicken skin"

===Noun===
'''[[piel]] [[de]] [[gallina]]'''
#{{esidiom}} [[goose bumps]]; raised [[skin]], usually on the [[neck]] or [[arms]] caused by [[cold]] or [[fear]]

